💧 AI Water Leakage System

An AI-powered IoT-based water leakage detection system that monitors water flow in real-time, detects abnormal usage patterns using Machine Learning, and sends instant alerts to prevent water wastage and infrastructure damage.

📌 Project Overview
This system continuously monitors water flow using IoT sensors connected to an ESP8266/ESP32 microcontroller. The collected data is sent to a cloud server where a Machine Learning model analyzes it to detect abnormal patterns (possible leaks).

If abnormal flow is detected:

An alert is generated

Notification is sent to the user

Data is stored for future analysis


